title: Patty Duke on Television - Comprehensive Video Collection
description:
I have created three Patty Duke torrents - one for her music, one for her films, and this one which contains television videos with or about Patty (other than films). In the Patty Duke Films torrent I have included theater movies, TV movies, the old-time live theater plays, mini-series, and anthology TV series where every episode had a unique story and different actors. Regular TV series, where the main characters return on each episode, are included in this torrent, but not in the Patty Duke films torrent.

Because I was always a big Patty Duke fan, I decided to put these torrents together in order to help preserve her legacy, and to make it possible for her fans to better appreciate all the outstanding work she did as an entertainer.

I spent a lot of time finding every worthwhile Patty Duke audio or video file I could, plus much more time organizing it all in logically structured layers of folders. Labelling everything properly was also very time consuming. I hope you all enjoy the contents of this and the other two Patty Duke torrents.
